17:10.836 --> 17:13.835
KYOTO ÜNİVERSİTESİ İÇİN!

17:13.836 --> 17:14.835
YETİMHANE MUCİZE BAHÇESİ

17:14.836 --> 17:16.836
YETİMHANE MUCİZE BAHÇESİ
Mucize Bahçesi?

17:17.836 --> 17:20.490
